Before September 2021, users were allowed to upload image watermarks but people longed for text watermarks. And on January 24, 2022, the company announced that users will be able to add text watermarks to documents. Apart from getting the ability to add text-based watermarks, the feature now ensures that the text watermark from files imported from other word processing apps will be preserved during the import or export process. Here is the full process of adding or editing a watermark. First, download the app from Google Play Store or Apple Store How to add the image watermark How to insert a text watermark Editing your watermark